*Tražili* smo stvari po celom gradu. (We were looking for things all over the town.)

*Tražili* su da se obezbedi dodatna pomoć. (They were asking for additional help.)

Deca su *tražila* ulicu na kojoj se nalazi škola. (The children were looking for the street where the school is located.)

*Tražila* sam pravu informaciju o odredištu. (I was looking for the right information about the destination.)

Mnogi su *tražili* da se ponovi ispit. (Many were asking for the exam to be repeated.)